Clement McCallin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clement_McCallin 0 Clement Schuyler McCallin (6 March 1913 – 7 August 1977) was a British actor from London. RADA trained, he made his stage debut in 1931, and worked extensively with the RSC and The Old Vic. He was married to actress Brenda Bruce, with whom he adopted a son. He was her second husband, and predeceased her, dying in 1977 in Stratford-upon-Avon, from unknown causes. Clement_Schuyler_McCallin ( 6_March_1913 – 7_August_1977 ) was a_British_actor from London .
